Package com.packt.webstore.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Address
    The class Address represents customer address information
    Cart
    The class Cart represents shopping Cart the class Cart provides methods for adding and removing items from shopping Cart and updating its total value
    CartItem
    The class CartItem represents separate element of Cart and includes the information about the product, the price and quantity the class CartItem provides method for updating total price for the cart item
    Customer
    The class Customer represents customer information
    Order
    The class Order represents customer order
    Product
    The class Product represents basic information about product, like code, name, price It is an Entity class.
    ProductData
    The class ProductData is an Entity class connected with the view PRODUCT_DATA in the database the ProductData reference is used in the repository layer by the method serving for displaying the details of the product with the information recorded in the database
    ProductStock
    The class ProductStock is an Entity class connected with the table PRODUCT_STOCK in the database the ProductStock reference is used in the repository layer for retrieving information from the database about the product stock
    ShippingDetail
    The class ShippingDetail represents basic customer information which is necessary for shipping the ordered products
